  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ensuring the highest quality end of life care</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cedar Village Hospice offers services focused on quality of life for terminally ill patients, those who no longer seek treatments to cure and who are expected to live six months of less.  These services provide comfort without aggressive treatment, focus on quality of life for patients and their families and are administered by an interdisciplinary team of professionals.  Pallative care is also offered and is based on relief of pain, stress, and other debilitating symptons of long term illness.</narrative>
  </description>
